{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Surface is a first person linear exploration game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game you simply walk your way to the end. The point is to immerse yourself in this world presented to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> There are no mechanics besides movement and looking around.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Being mysterious by design the story isn't told explicitly, everything is up to interpretation, all you know is that you want to reach the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448840/extras/Screenshot_22.png?t=1739356652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While the game does not contain monsters, the ambience and environments will invoke feelings of unease and even dread.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448840/extras/buildings.png?t=1739356652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every sound, model and script was crafted by me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448840/extras/danger.png?t=1739356652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>You have lived since birth in remote region of the megastructure, its not clear anymore how vast are its borders, you just want to see the surface once.</i></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739356652","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448840/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739356652","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3448840/1d0cbe68b0ba9d0a35c786185316e494deb11aef/capsule_